title: Karnataka
description: Specializes in South Indian cuisine, but also serves some North Indian dishes. Many vegan options (request your meal without ghee or paneer). Located on the second story of a multi-floor building just to the north of the Indian Oil building. The entrance is a staircase facing Aurobindo Marg.
streetAddress: 60/5, Yusuf Sarai Market, Aurobindo Marg, Green Park
